{"tid":287732,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[改詞MV] (原:春秋) 誰甘願被控制過去 誰就被控制未來","createTime":"2017-06-17T15:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T08:05:08.000Z","uid":35769,"like":49,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01a352aba169768902fcca78ee42a2942632d4db","tid":287732,"uid":35769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T15:53:22.000Z","msg":"一年前係舊登出詞 輾轉間一年後係連登出MV 實在恍如隔世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  在此感謝各位有份參與此作品既巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n// 歷史從來由勝利者及當權者定義  但任由真相被掩埋的每一位平凡人  其實都是幫兇  兇手與幫兇  都是千古罪人 // <br />\n<br />\n《千古罪人》<br />\n<br />\n原曲：春秋<br />\n原唱：張敬軒<br />\n原詞：林夕 <br />\n作曲：Edmond Tsang <br />\n編曲：C.Y. Kong <br />\n監製：C.Y. Kong / 張敬軒 <br />\n<br />\n主唱：柒菇碌叔叔<br />\n改詞：單機無雙 <br />\n混音：雪人也出火<br />\nMV：夏杉平<br />\n<br />\n往日誰真假對調<br />\n蒼生已分不清了 <br />\n寧願再盲目去相信直覺 <br />\n服從就免除紛擾 <br />\n<br />\n勝利時青史已定 <br />\n挫敗時已負污名 <br />\n何謂正義其實誰人又去編定 <br />\n縱然心知 卻願噤聲 <br />\n<br />\n真相不要問 無謂揭示殘酷未了現實的不堪 <br />\n<br />\n*葬下了日記先將春秋收進了墓地 <br />\n往後再定意為了治理編撰劇情愚弄這地 <br />\n聞說在世間 實情是誘惑與禁忌 <br />\n真相從無法推理 <br />\n<br />\n已沒法洞見駕馭歷史的天氣 <br />\n已沒法避免鹿馬亦會天天分到這樣兒戲 <br />\n繽紛中 誰想起 <br />\n這春秋 隨天氣 <br />\n只知道世事 似極美 <br />\n<br />\n倘若難知清往事 <br />\n去明瞭要待天時 <br />\n來日再發現從前被抹去的字 <br />\n弄人心思 有些暗示 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*葬下了日記先將春秋收進了墓地 <br />\n往後再定意為了治理編撰劇情愚弄這地 <br />\n聞說在世間 實情是誘惑與禁忌 <br />\n真相從無法推理 <br />\n<br />\n已沒法洞見駕馭歷史的天氣 <br />\n已沒法避免鹿馬亦會天天分到這樣兒戲 <br />\n繽紛中 誰想起 <br />\n這春秋 隨天氣 <br />\n只知道世事 似極美 <br />\n<br />\n哪願記起 <br />\n漠視了善惡遠走尚有快樂餘地 <br />\n<br />\n再沒有遇上真假之分闖進這天地 <br />\n也沒有道理為了讀破深藏玄機甚至死 <br />\n天生只知道勢利 <br />\n從不愛探索禁忌 <br />\n真與偽何從梳理 <br />\n閉著眼自我放任自欺的福氣 <br />\n閉著眼自會望遍歷遍一生感覺這樣完美 <br />\n天真的誰想起 <br />\n失蹤的是真理 <br />\n也許要確定你是你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nlink<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <a href=\"https://youtu.be/SuqBIpUAwIQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSuqBIpUAwIQ&d=K5fC9J%2FDBXU5QSe0Qq%2F4kjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=c4029fc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SuqBIpUAwIQ</a>"},{"pid":"40c0cf8a6c7bd1d12ec3da40f33d3a3dfc61d754","tid":287732,"uid":24945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T15:58:07.000Z","msg":"留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64887b5371ff01ecca67dd5b804cc8877c69d520","tid":287732,"uid":15524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T15:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a0348c4e72330ef2f921d60ec4bef9bf16a322","tid":287732,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T16:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dddaca50b3a668bfc507f83ba041c4ccc6425dd","tid":287732,"uid":4565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T16:14:08.000Z","msg":"面對歷史嗰種無力真係世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c03ee36b8046a4901817d4a32160c094e600dc3","tid":287732,"uid":39666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T16:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82282804e246f66a0a27160ce0e497c78a974ff4","tid":287732,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T16:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae23c1ceaf3cd0e9337b3077defd486fd43e153","tid":287732,"uid":1848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"